<chapter>
<title>Removable Documentation</title>
<section>
<title>What is Removable Documentation?</title>
<body>

<p>
<e>Removable Documentation</e> is documentation that is <e>really</e> 
outdated. The reason can be:
</p>

<ul>
<li>Outdated because unmaintained</li>
<li>Outdated because irrelevant</li>
</ul>

</body>
</section>
